Yunyi Ru

Biography

Yunyi Ru is a 2nd year masters student in the Molecular Microbiology and Immunology department of Johns Hopkins Bloomberg School of Public Health.

Yunyi currently works as a graduate student researcher at The Pekosz Lab on virology, and a research assistant at R3ISE Center) on responsive science communication.

Education

Johns Hopkins University | Baltimore, MD

ScM in Molecular Microbiology and Immunology | August 2023 - May 2025

Duke Kunshan University/Duke University | Kunshan, China/Durham, NC

B.S. in Cell and Molecular Biology (Dual Degree) | August 2019 - May 2023

Experience

Research

The Pekosz Lab, Johns Hopkins University | Graduate Student Researcher | October 2023 - Present

  • Isolated and characterized lab-adapted and circulating respiratory syncytial virus using various molecular biology and genetics methods.

The Lin Lab, Duke Kunshan University | Undergraduate Student Researcher | October 2021 - May 2023

  • Monitored and analyzed changes in antibiotic resistance gene prevalence in a local shallow lake over the year.

iGEM Competition 2022, Duke Kunshan University | Team Leader | December 2021 - October 2022

  • Designed an engineered bacteria strain by molecular cloning and protein expression.

Global Health Resource Center, Duke Kunshan University | Undergraduate Student Researcher | August 2020 - December 2020

  • Conducted surveys and interviews to assess the current situation of chronic disease management and control in 4 local communities.

Others

R3ISE Center, Johns Hopkins University | Research Assistant | October 2023 - Present

  • Initiated the R3 Read Today project by selecting and presenting content on important topics related to responsible scientific practices for science communication on X and Instagram.

Academic Resource Center, Duke Kunshan University | Teaching Assistant | October 2021 - December 2021

HOB Biotech Group Suzhou Co., Ltd | R&D Intern | July 2021 - August 2021

Intramural Global Health Case Competition, Duke Kunshan University | Team Leader | March 2021

Crystal Pharmatech Co., Ltd | R&D Intern | May 2020 - June 2020

Fun Fact

Yunyi is a fan of alt/indie music and enjoys playing the electric guitar in her free time.
